{"type":"message","id":"c4bee346","parentId":"24988e34","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:25:28.244Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-24 05:25 EDT] Phase 1: Supervised pre-training (2000 ep)\n ep 0: loss=5.7507 acc=0.000 route_ce=1.1545 div=0.0561 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 occ=17.3\n ep 200: loss=2.1594 acc=0.900 route_ce=1.1139 div=0.0601 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 occ=17.3\n ep 400: loss=2.1999 acc=0.850 route_ce=1.0707 div=0.0622 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 occ=17.3\n ep 600: loss=2.4640 acc=0.800 route_ce=1.0713 div=0.0624 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 occ=17.3\n ep 800: loss=2.6756 acc=0.750 route_ce=1.0639 div=0.0624 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 occ=17.3\n ep 1000: loss=2.5505 acc=0.800 route_ce=1.0623 div=0.0625 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 occ=17.3\n ep 1200: loss=2.4160 acc=0.800 route_ce=1.0556 div=0.0625 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 occ=17.3\n ep 1400: loss=2.0623 acc=0.900 route_ce=1.0562 div=0.0625 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 occ=17.3\n ep 1600: loss=2.7016 acc=0.750 route_ce=1.0496 div=0.0625 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 occ=17.3\n ep 1800: loss=2.0982 acc=0.850 route_ce=1.0606 div=0.0625 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 occ=17.3\n ep 1999: loss=2.1107 acc=0.850 route_ce=1.0569 div=0.0625 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 occ=17.3\n Phase 1 done in 785s\n\nPhase 2: Imitation learning (5000 ep)\n ep 0: loss=2.4629 acc=0.800 route_ce=1.0642 margin=0.0000 wr=0.11 rd=0.11 skip=0.79 blkd=0.00\n ep 500: loss=5.0441 acc=0.000 route_ce=1.0544 margin=0.0000 wr=0.29 rd=0.00 skip=0.71 blkd=0.71\n\nCLOSER I THINK"}],"timestamp":1774344328239}}
